text_2.eng:
@data.characters.f1_daughter_6.name: “Can I use your phone to play games?“

@data.characters.f1_mother.name: “Sure! But let’s set some household rules for using gadgets together. What do you think would be a fair rule?“

@data.characters.f1_mother.name: “It is important that you get your homework done so you can do well in school. Let’s make a rule about watching TV so that you have enough time for homework, too.”

@data.characters.f1_daughter_6.name: “Okay, @data.characters.f1_mother.name.”

